title: Mortal Kombat 1 - How to Play Omni-Man in 2 Minutes
description:
Learn Omni-Man fast! Here's our guide on how to play Omni-Man in Mortal Kombat 1 in just two minutes. This guide will give you an overview of how Omni-Man's playstyle, some go to normals and how to use them, a couple of note worthy special moves, and then a handful of damaging bread and butter combos that you should practice in training mode.

#IGN #Gaming #MortalKombat1

title: Invincible Presents: Atom Eve - Official Gameplay Trailer
description:
Invincible Presents: Atom Eve is a 2D story-rich visual novel action-adventure game developed by Terrible Posture Games. Check out the gameplay trailer for Invincible Presents: Atom Eve to see what to expect. 

Players will embody the role of super-hero Atom Eve and dictate her decisions to alter her path however the player deems fit. Develop her powers, engage in comic book-style combat, and experience an original narrative in a visually stunning world. Invincible Presents: Atom Eve is launching on November 14 for PC with the game being available on Amazon Prime Gaming for free from November 14 through November 21.

#IGN #Invincible #Gaming

title: Zenless Zone Zero - Official Equalizing Test Teaser Trailer
description: Get another look at Zenless Zone Zero in this latest trailer for the upcoming urban fantasy action RPG from HoYoverse. Zenless Zone Zero will be available on PC and mobile.

title: Predecessor - Official PlayStation Closed Beta Announcement Trailer
description:
Check out the latest Predecessor trailer to see the characters and more from this upcoming third-person action MOBA game. Predecessor will be available on PC and consoles, and a PlayStation Closed Beta test will begin on December 5, 2023.

In Predecessor, teams of five join arms in battle as they fight for glory on the battlefield against enemy heroes on a traditional three-lane map featuring an interactive jungle, epic monsters, and more.

#IGN #Gaming #PlayStation

title: Terrifier 3 - Official Teaser Trailer (2024) Damien Leone
description:
Watch the chilling teaser trailer for Terrifier 3, an upcoming horror film that sees the return of Art the Clown. In the third installment of writer/director Damien Leone’s breakout horror film, Art the Clown is set to unleash chaos on the unsuspecting residents of Miles County as they peacefully drift off to sleep on Christmas Eve. 

Terrifier 3 opens in theaters nationwide on October 25, 2024.

#IGN #Horror #Movies

title: Robots at Midnight - Official Reveal Trailer
description:
Take a look at the sci-fi world of Robots at Midnight in this announcement trailer for the upcoming action RPG that's set in a 1980s Cassette Futurist world.

Robots at Midnight follows Zoe, a scrappy and unlikely hero, as she searches and battles her way through the world of Yob, uncovering its secrets. Once a luxury destination now in ruins, Yob is an uninviting place overrun by robots – some friendly and others dangerous, and many that have begun to evolve, evoking questions of what it means to be human.

Robots at Midnight will be available in 2024 on PC and Xbox Series X/S consoles, with other platforms to follow.

#IGN #Gaming #Games

title: The Garfield Movie - Official Trailer (2024) Chris Pratt, Samuel L. Jackson, Hannah Waddingham
description:
Check out the trailer for The Garfield Movie. The upcoming animated film stars Chris Pratt (as the voice of Garfield), Samuel L. Jackson, Hannah Waddingham, Ving Rhames, Nicholas Hoult, Cecily Strong, Harvey Guillén, Brett Goldstein, and Bowen Yang.

Garfield (voiced by Chris Pratt), the world-famous, Monday-hating, lasagna-loving indoor cat, is about to have a wild outdoor adventure! After an unexpected reunion with his long-lost father – scruffy street cat Vic (voiced by Samuel L. Jackson) – Garfield and his canine friend Odie are forced from their perfectly pampered life into joining Vic in a hilarious, high-stakes heist.

The Garfield Movie is produced by John Cohen, Broderick Johnson, Andrew A. Kosove, Steven P. Wegner, Craig Sost, Namit Malhotra, and Crosby Clyse. Jim Davis, Bridget McMeel, David Reynolds, Scott Parish, Carl Rogers, Simon Hedges, Chris Pflug, Louis Koo, Steve Sarowitz, Justin Baldwin, and Peter Luo serve as executive producers. The screenplay is by Paul A. Kapl
